title: Ep. #88: Catching Up: Irene Kim
description:
This week, model/entrepreneur/KCON presenter Irene Kim catches up with Eric for the first time in three years! Find out how she snuck into a Marc Jacobs fashion show before her modeling years, what her brand IRENEISGOOD is all about, and why she doesn't consider herself an "influencer."

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.

Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios
